text.tspan: The labels on the right are hidden
Reference plot: al plots generated should have the same size, font size and lable size.
Two y axes with respective color and labels are used. In case you do not want two display the second y axis simply use opacity=0 on it, but
do not delete it. Besides, the format for the two y axis are "%2.0 f" and "%2.1f respectively". However, the number of minor ticks can be changed
in Gnuplot at the moment of creating the graph. You save the plot in .sgv format and resize it here in Inkscape.
Watch out ! All graphs below have second y axis but it is hidden
